Academic and sport stars got to shine during Elica Primary School’s annual prize giving ceremony held at a hospitality venue in the city on Friday. Trophies and certificates of achievement were presented to the top academic performers in acknowledgement of their continuous commitment towards achieving success.
Salome Mapea, Best Sport Achiever of all Times with 2019 Victor Ludorum, Mokge­thwa Madisha and Victrix Ludorum Nkhenzani Hlangwani.
Kgetho Chuene, Grade 1, Fatima Dipone, Grade 2 and Morongwa Dikgole, Grade 3 are the top achievers.
Excited Grade R learners ahead of their graduation ceremony.